      <title>德国预计到 2028 年税收收入将减少 420 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/germany-sees-42-billion-less-in-federal-tax-income-through-2028</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国联邦政府预计到 2028 年税收收入将比 10 月份的估计减少 416 亿欧元（452 亿美元），这可能会使明年预算的谈判变得更加复杂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/germany-sees-42-billion-less-in-federal-tax-income-through-2028</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 13:06:40 GMT</pubDate>
